<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Hail fellow Mages.  I have made lvl 12 about a week ago, and now I'm lvl 14.  My problem is ever since I bought my lvl 12 pet spells, I haven't been able to get a yellow con pet at lvl 12, and at 14 I didn't get a pet that conned even to me.  I've tried over a hundred times to summon the highest conned pet, but still no luck.  Is it just that I have bad luck with it, or has any other of my fellow Mages have been having this problem?  Could it be a bug?  I would like any info that could help me out.  Thanx.</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
