<td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="5" cellpadding="5" align="CENTER">
<tr>
<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">At lower levels, there are three possibilities for pet summons.  I am not sure how it works at higher levels, but I can tell you at level 29 I could not summon an even con pet using the level 29 spell.  The higher you get, the lower level your pets get in relation to you.  At level 12, it is possible to summon a level 11, 12, or 13 pet.  Since you waited until level 14 to do your test, all of them turned up blue because the highest possible was 13, which is blue to you.  If you had done your test at 12 or 13 you would have noticed even cons, and at 12 yellow cons.  Hope this helps, good luck.<p>

Kjata Holythunder<br>
Magician of Tunare</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
