<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Get used to it. At higher lvls you will only see blue pets. I'm lvl 40 and havn't seen an even pet for quite some time now. At current most of my pets or high 20's low 30's lvl. And from talking to high 50's lvl almost all of theirs are greens. But that doesn't mean our pets are weak. Just have to know each pets str's and weakness, that teamed with the power behind our DD's is what makes a mage truely great.<p>

Velyn Brytstar<p>

"Cry Havoc, and let slip the dogs of WAR"</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
